---
<section class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 py-20 lg:py-24">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-screen-xl">
    <div class="max-w-screen-lg text-center mx-auto mb-8 lg:mb-16">
      <h2 class="mb-4 text-3xl lg:text-4xl tracking-tight font-extrabold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
        Solusi Cerdas untuk Bisnis Anda
      </h2>
